nd Caribbean traditions, LAJOUPA isn't just a place to eat - it's a place to feel.\n\nAt the Bar Corner, sip bold rum cocktails while Afrobeat and Latin rhythms fill the room.\n\nChilling Lounges with tribal decor and lush greenery invite you to unwind under soft lights and great company.\n\nFrom the Kitchen, rich spices meet fresh seafood, slow-cooked meats, and fire-grilled flavours - echoing centuries of Creole tradition, reimagined for today.\n\nWhether you're here to dance, relax, or indulge, LAJOUPA brings you a taste of culture, community, and celebration.","address":"Rue du Souffleur Mahebourg, Mauritius","phone":"+230 5290 1268","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4102622,57.7098741","image":"https://onestophalal.com/cdn/shop/articles/beef_samosa-1697330921061_1200x.jpg?v=1697330957","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"Mon to Tue,Thur to Sun：18:30-22:30  - Wed：Closed all day "},{"id":"e41jy9ge","nameFr":"Avalon Golf Estate","nameEn":"Avalon Golf Estate","descFr":"Domaine de golf haut de gamme dans un cadre tropical. Parcours 9 trous et restaurant avec vue panoramique.","descEn":"Upscale golf estate in a tropical setting. 9-hole course and restaurant with panoramic views.","address":" Bois Cheri Road, Bois Cheri 60203","phone":"+230 430 5800","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4369266,57.5141254","image":"https://avalon.mu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Fotolia_176339213_Subscription_Monthly_M-compressor.jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"WEEK DAYS 8h30 - 16h30 - WEEKEND 07:30 AM to 5:30 PM"}],"coverPhoto":"https://voilahotel.mu/media/5yfhwzvq/lcr-dining.jpg"},{"id":"plages","nameFr":"Les Plages dans la Région","nameEn":"Beaches in the Region","icon":"🏖️","color":"#1b6ca8","items":[{"id":"9xpsj165","nameFr":"La Cambuse Beach","nameEn":"La Cambuse Beach","descFr":"Plage sauvage et préservée face au lagon turquoise. Idéale pour se baigner loin des foules, avec une vue imprenable sur l'horizon.","descEn":"Unspoilt wild beach facing the turquoise lagoon. Perfect for swimming away from the crowds, with stunning views to the horizon.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4534568,57.6995888","image":"https://cdn.getyourguide.com/img/location/5d30467254bdd.jpeg/99.jpg","distance":"8 minutes","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"e0qvml9z","nameFr":"Shandrani Beach","nameEn":"Shandrani Beach","descFr":"Plage cachée 5 étoiles bordée de filaos, aux eaux calmes et cristallines, offrant un cadre tropical exceptionnel.\nSituée devant l'hôtel Shandrani Beachcomber Resort & Spa, cette plage séduit par son atmosphère paisible et préservée. Le sable fin, les nuances turquoise du lagon et l'ombre naturelle des filaos créent un décor idyllique, parfait pour la détente, la baignade et les couchers de soleil tropicaux. Protégée par le récif, la mer y reste généralement calme, idéale pour profiter pleinement de la beauté authentique du sud-est mauricien.","descEn":"Hidden 5-star beach lined with filao trees, featuring calm crystal-clear waters and an exceptional tropical setting.\nLocated in front of Shandrani Beachcomber Resort & Spa, this beach charms visitors with its peaceful and unspoiled atmosphere. The fine white sand, turquoise lagoon, and natural shade from the filaos create an idyllic backdrop, perfect for relaxation, swimming, and tropical sunsets. Protected by the coral reef, the sea remains calm most of the time, making it an ideal spot to fully enjoy the authentic beauty of southeastern Mauritius.\n","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4453272,57.7029955","image":"https://q-xx.bstatic.com/xdata/images/hotel/max500/270756106.jpg?k=d062c68866f40c3b635075bf0b8d1a46f5fea8bbb7a767b111577981fb323a37&o=","distance":"8 minutes","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"51dynmfh","nameFr":"La plade de Blue Bay","nameEn":"Blue Bay Beach","descFr":"La plage de Blue Bay est l'une des plus belles plages de l'île Maurice. Située sur la côte sud-est, elle est réputée pour son sable blanc, ses eaux turquoise et son lagon cristallin. La plage est bordée de filaos qui offrent de l'ombre aux visiteurs. Blue Bay est également célèbre pour son parc marin, où l'on peut observer de magnifiques coraux et une grande variété de poissons tropicaux. C'est un lieu idéal pour la baignade, la plongée avec tuba et les excursions en bateau. Son cadre paisible et sa beauté naturelle attirent aussi bien les habitants que les touristes.","descEn":"Blue Bay Beach is one of the most beautiful beaches in Mauritius. Located on the south-eastern coast of the island, it is famous for its white sand, turquoise waters, and crystal-clear lagoon. The beach is lined with casuarina trees that provide shade for visitors. Blue Bay is also well known for its marine park, where visitors can admire beautiful coral reefs and a wide variety of tropical fish. It is an ideal place for swimming, snorkeling, and boat excursions. Its peaceful atmosphere and natural beauty make it a favorite destination for both locals and tourists.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4441928,57.7164692","image":"https://vacancesmaurice.com/content/images/gallery/1607/blue-bay-beach%20(1).jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"jtal4nlj","nameFr":"La plade de Pointe D'esny","nameEn":"Pointe D'esny Beach","descFr":"La plage de Pointe d'Esny est l'une des plus belles plages de la côte sud-est de l'île Maurice. Réputée pour son sable blanc et son lagon aux eaux turquoise et cristallines, elle offre un cadre paisible et préservé. Cette plage est idéale pour la baignade, les promenades en bord de mer et les activités nautiques. Située à proximité du village du Bouchon, Pointe d'Esny bénéficie d'un environnement naturel exceptionnel et d'une atmosphère authentique. Les visiteurs peuvent profiter de magnifiques paysages côtiers tout en découvrant le charme des villages du sud-est mauricien.","descEn":"Pointe d'Esny Beach is one of the most beautiful beaches on the south-eastern coast of Mauritius. Known for its white sandy shore and its crystal-clear turquoise lagoon, it offers a peaceful and unspoiled environment. The beach is perfect for swimming, seaside walks, and water activities. Located close to the village of Le Bouchon, Pointe d'Esny enjoys an exceptional natural setting and an authentic atmosphere. Visitors can admire stunning coastal scenery while experiencing the charm of the villages in the south-east of Mauritius.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4265134,57.7263732","image":"https://a0.muscache.com/im/pictures/c756ee8f-49ce-463b-9997-8e4f60ef33c4.jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"533il2qg","nameFr":"Pomponette Plage Publique","nameEn":"Pomponette Public Beach","descFr":"La plage de Pomponette est une plage sauvage et préservée située sur la côte sud-est de l'île Maurice, entre Mahébourg et Souillac. Réputée pour sa beauté naturelle, elle est bordée de filaos et offre une vue magnifique sur l'océan Indien. Son sable doré et son environnement paisible en font un lieu apprécié des amoureux de la nature et de ceux qui recherchent la tranquillité. Bien que la mer puisse parfois être agitée, la plage de Pomponette reste un endroit idéal pour se détendre, pique-niquer et admirer les paysages côtiers exceptionnels de la région.","descEn":"Pomponette Beach is a wild and unspoiled beach located on the south-eastern coast of Mauritius, between Mahébourg and Souillac. Known for its natural beauty, it is lined with casuarina trees and offers stunning views of the Indian Ocean. Its golden sand and peaceful surroundings make it a favorite spot for nature lovers and visitors seeking tranquility. Although the sea can sometimes be rough, Pomponette Beach remains an ideal place to relax, enjoy a picnic, and admire the region's spectacular coastal scenery.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.5164027,57.4766148","image"