ties","icon":"🤿","color":"#7b5ea7","items":[{"id":"ahmyl2ka","nameFr":"Angel Cruises Bateau Rapide","nameEn":"Angel Cruises Speedboat","descFr":"Excursions en speedboat vers Blue Bay, Ile aux Cerfs et les ilots. Snorkeling, barbecue sur plage privée","descEn":"Speedboat excursions to Blue Bay, Ile aux Cerfs and the islets. Snorkelling, barbecue on a private beach","address":"","phone":"+2305472 9027","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4473342,57.7060676","image":"https://scontent.fmru7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/474714827_2668360126696069_3592696779050479743_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=cc71e4&_nc_ohc=yABvOEAktuUQ7kNvwHOn8px&_nc_oc=AdrkX9mcuarg2Bo9IA-pImfHJ6BjndGT3dkUaGiKAkrNxRRQVJMq5ljN_ajdOOaPNiw&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fmru7-1.fna&_nc_gid=_3KB9cD2whG9doxuKH4DQw&_nc_ss=7b289&oh=00_Af5iuyEGR1ogQ6W_XTo3zQD4SO8ScDDg6byU1_6ZAKvCOA&oe=6A20C171","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"h72cpgat","nameFr":"Quad Bike - Pont Naurel Quad Bike","nameEn":"Quad Bike - Pont Naurel Quad Bike","descFr":"Aventure en quad à travers les champs de canne à sucre jusqu'au Pont Naturel. Sensations fortes et paysages sauvages.","descEn":"Quad bike adventure through sugar cane fields to Pont Naturel. Thrills and wild landscapes in the south.","address":"Mon Desert Mon Tresor, Ex Sugar Factory, MU, Plaine Magnien 51512","phone":"+2305941 8818","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4533487,57.6799323","image":"https://vacancesmaurice.com/content/images/gallery/1483/half-day-quad-bike-trip-in-the-south-of-mauritius%20(6).jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"8h30 - 17h"},{"id":"5hdhstbp1","nameFr":"Casela Nature Parks","nameEn":"Casela Nature Parks","descFr":"Casela Nature Parks est l'un des plus grands parcs d'aventure et de nature de l'île Maurice, situé sur la côte ouest à Cascavelle, près de Flic-en-Flac. Le parc s'étend sur plusieurs centaines d'hectares et combine safari, zoo, activités d'aventure et expériences avec les animaux.\n\nOn peut y observer de nombreux animaux comme des lions, zèbres, girafes, rhinocéros, autruches, tortues géantes et une grande variété d'oiseaux. Casela est surtout connu pour ses activités uniques comme le safari en 4x4, la tyrolienne, les balades en quad et même la marche avec les lions encadrée par des professionnels.\n\nC'est une destination très populaire pour les familles, les groupes et les amateurs de sensations fortes.","descEn":"Casela Nature Parks is one of the largest adventure and wildlife parks in Mauritius, located on the west coast at Cascavelle near Flic-en-Flac. The park spans several hundred hectares and combines safari experiences, a zoo, adventure activities, and animal encounters.\n\nVisitors can see animals such as lions, zebras, giraffes, rhinos, ostriches, giant tortoises, and many bird species. Casela is especially famous for unique activities like 4x4 safaris, ziplining, quad biking, and even supervised lion walks.\n\nIt is a very popular destination for families, groups, and adventure lovers.","address":"Royal Road, Cascavelle, Flic-en-Flac, Île Maurice","phone":"+230 401 6500","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=Casela+Nature+Parks+Mauritius","image":"https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/2a/47/38/76/presenting-you-our-new.jpg?w=2400&h=1800&s=1","distance":"","priceLevel":"Rs 900 - Rs 2,500","openHours":"09h00 - 17h00"},{"id":"ltzoq45z","nameFr":"We Glide - Kitesurf & Wingfoil","nameEn":"We Glide - Kitesurf & Wingfoil","descFr":"Ecole et club de kitesurf dans les meilleures conditions de vent de l'ile. Cours débutants et location de matériel.","descEn":"Kitesurfing school and club in the island's best wind conditions. Beginner lessons and equipment rental.","address":"Pointe d'esny MU, Mahébourg 50810","phone":"+230 5511 4777","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4200943,57.7209395","image":"https://solanabeach.mu/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/KA88711-1536x960-1.jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"py9m0m8kd","nameFr":"La Vanille Nature Park","nameEn":"La Vanille Nature Park","descFr":"La Vanille Nature Park est l'une des attractions les plus populaires du sud de l'île Maurice. Situé dans un cadre tropical luxuriant, le parc abrite la plus grande collection de tortues géantes d'Aldabra de l'océan Indien. Les visiteurs peuvent également découvrir des crocodiles du Nil, des singes, des chauves-souris géantes, des geckos, des insectes rares ainsi qu'une riche flore tropicale. Le parc offre une expérience éducative et familiale unique, idéale pour les amoureux de la nature et de la faune mauricienne.","descEn":"La Vanille Nature Park is one of the most popular attractions in southern Mauritius. Set in a lush tropical environment, the park is home to the largest collection of Aldabra giant tortoises in the Indian Ocean. Visitors can also discover Nile crocodiles, monkeys, giant fruit bats, geckos, rare insects, and a rich variety of tropical plants. The park offers a unique educational and family-friendly experience, making it a must-visit destination for nature and wildlife enthusiasts.","address":"La Vanille Nature Park, Royal Road, Rivière des Anguilles, Mauritius","phone":"+230 626 2503","mapLink":"https://www.google.com/maps?q=La+Vanille+Nature+Park+Mauritius","image":"https://taxiservicemauritius.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/1-9.jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"Rs 500-700 adults, Rs 250-400/enfant-kids","openHours":"09h00 - 17h00"},{"id":"o5xghn2r","nameFr":"DS Adventures","nameEn":"DS Adventures","descFr":"Activités d'aventure et excursions sur mesure dans le sud de Maurice. Randonnées, kayak et découverte de la nature locale.","descEn":"Adventure activities and tailor-made excursions in the south of Mauritius. Hiking, kayaking and local nature discovery.","address":"MU, 1 Ayodhya Lane, Trois Boutiques 52001","phone":"+2305977 0006","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4513559,57.6514577","image":"https://media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/attractions-splice-spp-720x480/11/65/a4/01.jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"9h -16hr30"},{"id":"ibrtyy74","nameFr":"Avalon Golf Estate","nameEn":"Avalon Golf Estate","descFr":"Domaine de golf haut de gamme dans un cadre tropical. Parcours 9 trous et restaurant avec vue panoramique.","descEn":"Upscale golf estate in a tropical setting. 9-hole course and restaurant with panoramic views.","address":"Bois Cheri Road, Bois Cheri 60203","phone":"+230430 5800","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4369266,57.5141254","image":"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/inntox6v/production/1dcc2187271c0e83951d82d1faf88679743ea4d5-1000x649.jpg?fp-x=0.5&fp-y=0.5&w=1536&h=864&fit=crop&auto=format","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"8h - 16:30/17h"},{"id":"rql3j2mpf","nameFr":"Dolphin Warriors","nameEn":"Dolphin Warriors","descFr":"Dolphin Warriors est une compagnie d'excursions en bateau basée sur la côte sud-ouest de l'île Maurice, à La Gaulette. Elle est spécialisée dans les sorties en mer pour observer et nager avec les dauphins dans leur habitat naturel.\n\nLes excursions commencent tôt le matin et incluent généralement la sortie en bateau à la recherche des dauphins, des sessions de snorkeling, et des arrêts sur des sites emblématiques comme le Crystal Rock et l'Île aux Bénitiers. Certaines formules proposent aussi un déjeuner barbecue sur la plage et des expériences personnalisées (sunset, pêche, excursions privées).\n\nC'est une activité très populaire à Maurice pour découvrir la faune marine et profiter des paysages de la côte ouest.","descEn":"Dolphin Warriors is a boat excursion company based on the south-west coast of Mauritius in La Gaulette. It specializes in dolphin watching and swimming experiences in their natural habitat.\n\nTrips usually start early in the morning and include boat excursions to spot dolphins, snorkeling sessions, and stops at iconic locations such as Crystal Rock and Île aux Bénitiers. Some packages also offer beach BBQ lunches and customized experiences (sunset trips, fishing, private charters).\n\nIt is a very popular activity in Mauritius for exploring marine wildlife and enjoying the scenic west coast.","address":"La Gaulette, Rivière Noire, Île Maurice","phone":"+230 5755 4175","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=Dolphin+Warrior+La+Gaulette+Mauritius","image":"https://mauritiusattractions.com/content/images/gallery/1470/swim-with-dolphin-2-5-hour-budget-trip%20(3).jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"Rs 1,500 - Rs 3,500","openHours":"05h30 - 06h00"}],"coverPhoto":"https://toursmauritius.mu/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/header-lion-safari.jpg"},{"id":"voir","nameFr":"Les Endroits à Voir","nameEn":"Places to See","icon":"👁️","color":"#f0a500","items":[{"id":"juu1gw72","nameFr":"Pont Naturel","nameEn":"Pont Naturel","descFr":"Arche naturelle spectaculaire sculptée par l'océan dans les roches volcaniques du sud. Site géologique unique et sauvage.","descEn":"Spectacular natural arch sculpted by the ocean in the volcanic rocks of the south. Unique and wild geological site.","address":"Carreau Accacia","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.480442,57.6693878","image":"https://vacancesmaurice.com/content/images/gallery/1620/pont-naturel-mauritius%20(2).jpg","distance":"22mins","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"clm2cndx","nameFr":"Blue Bay Marine Park","nameEn":"Blue Bay Marine Park","descFr":"Parc marin protégé avec 38 espèces de coraux et 72 espèces de poissons. Idéal pour le snorkeling et les balades en bateau à fond de verre.","descEn":"Protected marine park with 38 coral species and 72 fish species. Ideal for snorkelling and glass-bottom boat trips.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4448478,57.709801","image":"https://dynamic-media.tacdn.com/media/photo-o/2f/1d/70/50/caption.jpg?w=1400&h=1000&s=1","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"iz7hbxf8","nameFr":"La Vallée de Ferney","nameEn":"La Vallée de Ferney","descFr":"Réserve naturelle de 200 hectares préservant la forêt endémique de l'île. Randonnées guidées, faune sauvage et paysages verdoyants.","descEn":"200-hectare nature reserve preserving the island's endemic forest. Guided hikes, wildlife and lush landscapes.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.3620088,57.7056026","image":"https://ferney.mu/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/VDF_00266-copy-1024x490.jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"iwpp4lg0","nameFr":"Musée National d'Histoire de Mahébourg","nameEn":"Mahebourg Museum","descFr":"Musée historique retraçant la bataille de Grand Port de 1810. Cartes anciennes, objets coloniaux et maquettes de navires.\n\nDécouvrez l'histoire fascinante de l'île Maurice à travers des artefacts coloniaux, des cartes anciennes, des vestiges de naufrages et un célèbre squelette de dodo. Installé dans une élégante demeure coloniale du XVIIIe siècle, ce musée retrace l'histoire maritime et culturelle de l'île.","descEn":"Historical museum telling the story of the 1810 Battle of Grand Port. Ancient maps, colonial artefacts and ship models.\n\nDécouvrez l'histoire fascinante de l'île Maurice à travers des artefacts coloniaux, des cartes anciennes, des vestiges de naufrages et un célèbre squelette de dodo. Installé dans une élégante demeure coloniale du XVIIIe siècle, ce musée retrace l'histoire maritime et culturelle de l'île.","address":"Royal Road, Mahébourg, Grand Port, Mauritius","phone":"+230631 9329","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4163245,57.7033301","image":"https://visaliv.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Mahebourg.jpg","distance":"10mins","priceLevel":"Free","openHours":"9h00-16h00"},{"id":"k8vfv2kt","nameFr":"Mahebourg Waterfront","nameEn":"Mahebourg Waterfront","descFr":"Promenade balnéaire animée avec vue sur les îlots de la baie. Restaurants, artisanat local et couchers de soleil magnifiques.","descEn":"Lively seaside promenade with views over the bay's islets. Restaurants, local crafts and magnificent sunsets.","address":"Mahebourg","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4050275,57.7097567","image":"https://media.istockphoto.com/id/158062068/photo/wooden-walkway-mauritius.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=s4uB89nhFRSr05mHuv2JRt1jjoJ7qL200_Ou2lkPEic=","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"56cdnt2v","nameFr":"La Vanille Nature Park","nameEn":"La Vanille Nature Park","descFr":"Parc naturel avec tortues géantes, crocodiles du Nil et lémuriens. Cadre tropical luxuriant, accessible à toute la famille.\n\nL'un des parcs animaliers les plus célèbres de Maurice. Découvrez plus de 1 000 tortues géantes d'Aldabra, des crocodiles du Nil, des lémuriens, des iguanes et une forêt tropicale luxuriante. Une sortie idéale pour les familles et les amoureux de la nature.","descEn":"Nature park with giant tortoises, Nile crocodiles and lemurs. Lush tropical setting, perfect for the whole family.\n\nOne of Mauritius' most famous wildlife parks. Discover over 1,000 giant Aldabra tortoises, Nile crocodiles, lemurs, iguanas and a lush tropical forest. A perfect outing for families and nature lovers.","address":"Senneville, Rivière des Anguilles 60602, Maurice","phone":"+230 626 2503","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.499475,57.563272","image":"https://mauritiusattractions.com/content/images/guide/i-341/la-vanille-nature-park%20(1).jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"Non résident adulte : Rs 975 Non résident enfant : Rs 685","openHours":"9h00 à 17h00"},{"id":"aokfyybg","nameFr":"Vallée Adventure Park","nameEn":"Vallée Adventure Park","descFr":"Parc d'aventure avec tyrolienne et quad dans la vallée de Ferney. Adrénaline garantie dans un cadre verdoyant.\n\nL'un des plus grands parcs d'aventure de Maurice. Découvrez les célèbres Terres des 23 Couleurs, des cascades spectaculaires, des ponts suspendus, des tyroliennes, du quad, du buggy et des panoramas exceptionnels sur les paysages sauvages du sud de l'île.","descEn":"Adventure park with zip-line and quad bikes in the Ferney Valley. Guaranteed thrills in a lush green setting.\n\nOne of the largest adventure parks in Mauritius. Discover the famous 23 Coloured Earth, breathtaking waterfalls, suspension bridges, zip lines, quad biking, buggy tours and spectacular views across the island's wild southern landscapes.","address":"","phone":"+230 660 4477","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4579232,57.4844716","image":"https://dynamic-media-cdn.tripadvisor.com/media/photo-o/2b/51/64/1d/caption.jpg?w=1200&h=-1&s=1","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"09h00 à 17h30"},{"id":"snenyzdt","nameFr":"Casela Nature Parks | Ile Maurice","nameEn":"Casela Nature Parks | Ile Maurice","descFr":"Le parc nature numéro 1 de Maurice avec lions, zèbres et rhinocéros. Marche avec les lions et safari en bus pour toute la famille.\n\nL'un des parcs de loisirs les plus populaires de Maurice. Profitez de safaris africains, tyroliennes géantes, ponts suspendus, quad, luge, interactions avec les animaux et vues spectaculaires sur la côte ouest. Une activité incontournable pour les familles et les amateurs d'aventure.","descEn":"Mauritius's number 1 nature park with lions, zebras and rhinos. Walk with lions and bus safari for the whole family.\n\nOne of Mauritius' most popular adventure and wildlife parks. Enjoy African safaris, giant zip lines, suspension bridges, quad biking, luge rides, animal encounters and breathtaking views over the west coast. A must visit attraction for families and adventure seekers.","address":"Royal Road, Cascavelle, Mauritius","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.2911477,57.4039949","image":"https://caselaparks.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mission-768x479.png","distance":"","priceLevel":"Rs.1000 - 5000","openHours":"09h00 à 17h00"},{"id":"jhuuxm7e","nameFr":"Ile Des Deux Cocos","nameEn":"Ile Des Deux Cocos","descFr":"Ilot privé classé Ramsar, accessible en bateau depuis Blue Bay. Eaux turquoises, snorkeling et pique-nique créole.\n\nÎle privée paradisiaque située au large de Blue Bay, réputée pour ses eaux turquoise, son parc marin protégé et sa magnifique villa coloniale. Profitez d'une journée all inclusive avec snorkeling, excursions en bateau à fond de verre, déjeuner buffet et détente sur l'une des plus belles îles du sud-est de Maurice.","descEn":"Private Ramsar-listed islet, accessible by boat from Blue Bay. Turquoise waters, snorkelling and Creole picnic.\n\nA stunning private island located off the coast of Blue Bay, famous for its turquoise lagoon, protected marine park and beautiful colonial villa. Enjoy an all inclusive day experience with snorkeling, glass bottom boat trips, buffet lunch and relaxation on one of the most beautiful islands in south east Mauritius.","address":"Ile Des Deux Cocos","phone":"+230 698 2727","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4487075,57.7109832","image":"https://www.ile-maurice.fr/images/2024/10/14/escapade-ile-des-deux-cocos_large.jpg","distance":"20mins","priceLevel":"Rs.3000 - 5000","openHours":"10h00 à 15h30"},{"id":"vuw75xi8","nameFr":"Lion Mountain hiking trail","nameEn":"Lion Mountain hiking trail","descFr":"Randonnée emblématique (564m) avec vue panoramique sur le lagon de Mahebourg. Environ 3h aller-retour, niveau modéré.\n\nL'une des plus belles randonnées du sud-est de Maurice. Grimpez jusqu'au sommet de la Montagne du Lion et profitez de vues spectaculaires sur Mahébourg, le lagon de Blue Bay, les îlots du Grand Port et la côte sauvage. Une randonnée idéale pour les amateurs de nature, de photographie et d'aventure.","descEn":"Iconic hike (564m) with panoramic views over the Mahebourg lagoon. About 3 hours return, moderate difficulty.\n\nOne of the most scenic hikes in south east Mauritius. Reach the summit of Lion Mountain and enjoy breathtaking views over Mahébourg, Blue Bay lagoon, the Grand Port islets and the island's wild coastline. Perfect for nature lovers, photographers and adventure seekers.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.3720852,57.7270345","image":"https://mauritiusattractions.com/content/images/gallery/1411/Lion%20Mountain%20Half-Day%20Guided%20Hike%20(5).jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"Best time to leave the house 6h00 et 8h00"},{"id":"b0xsat7t","nameFr":"Ile aux Aigrettes","nameEn":"Ile aux Aigrettes","descFr":"Ile-réserve naturelle de 26 hectares préservant l'écosystème original de Maurice. Tortues géantes et oiseaux endémiques.\n\nRéserve naturelle protégée située au large de Mahébourg, l'Île aux Aigrettes abrite les dernières forêts côtières indigènes de Maurice. Découvrez des espèces rares comme les tortues géantes d'Aldabra, le pigeon rose et une flore unique au monde lors d'une visite guidée au cœur d'un important projet de conservation.","descEn":"26-hectare nature reserve island preserving Mauritius's original ecosystem. Giant tortoises and endemic birds.\n\nLocated off the coast of Mahébourg, Île aux Aigrettes is a protected nature reserve home to Mauritius' last remaining dry coastal forest. Discover rare species such as giant Aldabra tortoises, pink pigeons and unique endemic plants during a guided eco tour through one of the island's most important conservation projects.","address":"Aigrette Island","phone":"+230 5258 8139","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.417984,57.7311238","image":"https://bonjourmaurice.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/ile-aux-aigrettes.jpg","distance":"","priceLevel":"Rs.135 - Rs.385","openHours":"Lun-Sam : 09h30, 10h00, 10h30, 13h30, 14h00 Dim : 09h30, 10h30"},{"id":"xm312fgq","nameFr":"Île aux Cerfs","nameEn":"Île aux Cerfs","descFr":"Ile paradisiaque dans le lagon de l'est, destination phare de Maurice. Eaux cristallines, sports nautiques et restaurants de bord de mer.\n\nL'une des îles les plus célèbres de Maurice, réputée pour ses plages de sable blanc, son immense lagon turquoise et ses nombreuses activités nautiques. Profitez du snorkeling, parachute ascensionnel, bouée tractée, excursions en catamaran ou simplement d'une journée détente dans un décor de carte postale.","descEn":"Paradise island in the eastern lagoon, Mauritius's flagship destination. Crystal-clear waters, water sports and beachside restaurants.\n\nOne of Mauritius' most famous islands, known for its white sandy beaches, crystal clear turquoise lagoon and wide range of water activities. Enjoy snorkeling, parasailing, tube rides, catamaran cruises or simply relax in a stunning tropical paradise.","address":"Île aux Cerfs, Trou d'Eau Douce, Flacq, Mauritius","phone":"+230 402 7400","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.2723538,57.8041107","image":"https://vacancesmaurice.com/content/images/nma-image/guide/36/ile-aux-cerfs-beach-0.jpg","distance":"35mins","priceLevel":"Rs 1 200 à Rs 4 500","openHours":""},{"id":"zpwbhqzd","nameFr":"Old Light House (île au phare)","nameEn":"Old Light House (île au phare)","descFr":"Phare historique sur un ilot du lagon de Mahebourg. Accessible en bateau, panorama exceptionnel et couchers de soleil.\n\nDécouvrez l'emblématique Île au Phare, un îlot historique situé dans le lagon du Grand Port. Connu pour son ancien phare datant du XIXe siècle, ce lieu offre des paysages spectaculaires entre falaises volcaniques, ruines historiques et eaux turquoise du sud-est mauricien. Accessible uniquement en bateau, c'est une excursion parfaite pour les amateurs d'histoire, de photographie et d'aventure.","descEn":"Historic lighthouse on a small islet in Mahebourg lagoon. Accessible by boat, exceptional panorama and sunsets.\n\nDiscover the iconic Old Lighthouse Island, a historic islet located in the Grand Port lagoon. Famous for its 19th century lighthouse, the island features dramatic volcanic cliffs, historical ruins and breathtaking turquoise waters. Accessible only by boat, it is a perfect excursion for history lovers, photographers and adventure seekers.","address":"","phone":"+230 5472 9027","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.3957788,57.7773863","image":"https://wpktirmzveoovxjqbqpq.supabase.co/storage/v1/render/image/public/images/ile-au-phare.jpg?width=1200&quality=75&format=origin","distance":"20mins boat","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"2lzxzsz8","nameFr":"Cascade Rochester Falls","nameEn":"Rochester Falls","descFr":"Cascade unique aux dalles volcaniques rectangulaires ressemblant à des colonnes de basalte. Paysage minéral et sauvage dans le sud.\n\nL'une des cascades les plus célèbres de Maurice, réputée pour ses impressionnantes falaises basaltiques rectangulaires sculptées naturellement par l'eau. Située au cœur d'une région verdoyante entourée de champs de canne à sucre, Rochester Falls est un lieu idéal pour la baignade, la photographie et la découverte de paysages naturels du sud de l'île.","descEn":"Unique waterfall with rectangular volcanic slabs resembling basalt columns. Wild, mineral landscape in the south.\n\nOne of Mauritius' most famous waterfalls, known for its unique rectangular basalt rock formations naturally shaped by water over time. Surrounded by lush greenery and sugar cane fields, Rochester Falls is a perfect spot for swimming, photography and exploring the island's natural beauty.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.5029835,57.5168288","image":"https://www.ilemaurice-tourisme.info/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Rochester-Falls2.jpg","distance":"30mins","priceLevel":"Free","openHours":""},{"id":"mjadw6ct","nameFr":"Grand Bassin Temple","nameEn":"Grand Bassin Temple","descFr":"Lac volcanique sacré et lieu de pèlerinage hindou le plus important de Maurice. Ambiance spirituelle intense et décor naturel.\n\nL'un des lieux les plus sacrés de Maurice. Situé dans le cratère d'un ancien volcan au cœur des montagnes, Grand Bassin est un lac sacré dédié à la religion hindoue. Entouré de temples colorés, de statues monumentales et d'une atmosphère paisible, ce site spirituel offre une immersion unique dans la culture mauricienne et des panoramas magnifiques sur la nature environnante.","descEn":"Sacred volcanic lake and most important Hindu pilgrimage site in Mauritius. Intense spiritual atmosphere and natural setting.\n\nOne of the most sacred places in Mauritius. Located inside an ancient volcanic crater surrounded by lush mountains, Grand Bassin is a holy lake dedicated to the Hindu faith. With its colorful temples, giant deity statues and peaceful atmosphere, it offers a unique cultural experience and beautiful views of the surrounding nature.","address":"Grand Bassin","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4183273,57.4934292","image":"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/maha-shivaratri-pilgrimage-grand-bassin-mauritius-grand-bassin-mauritius-february-devotees-gather-grand-bassin-434829461.jpg","distance":"45mins","priceLevel":"Free","openHours":""},{"id":"wa7ng6jl","nameFr":"Tamarind Falls / 7 Cascades","nameEn":"Tamarind Falls / 7 Cascades","descFr":"Les célèbres 7 Cascades en pleine forêt tropicale. Randonnée et baignade dans des piscines naturelles, une expérience inoubliable.\n\nExplorez l'un des plus beaux sites naturels de Maurice avec Tamarind Falls, aussi connue sous le nom des 7 Cascades. Cette randonnée spectaculaire traverse une forêt tropicale luxuriante, plusieurs cascades naturelles et des piscines d'eau douce parfaites pour la baignade. Une expérience incontournable pour les amoureux de nature, d'aventure et de paysages sauvages.","descEn":"The famous 7 Cascades in tropical forest. Hiking and swimming in natural pools - an unforgettable experience.\n\nDiscover one of Mauritius' most breathtaking natural attractions at Tamarind Falls, also known as Seven Cascades. This spectacular hike takes you through lush tropical forest, multiple waterfalls and natural freshwater pools ideal for swimming. A must do experience for nature lovers, adventure seekers and hiking enthusiasts.","address":"","phone":"+23057184966","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.3547247,57.4664171","image":"https://explora.mu/media/k2/items/cache/793ea701476d5db2a4fd8cf1e0bf5880_XL.jpg?t=20210913_135249","distance":"36mins","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"244t90pu","nameFr":"Bois Cheri Tea Factory","nameEn":"Bois Cheri Tea Factory","descFr":"La plus ancienne plantation de thé de Maurice, en activité depuis 1892. Visite guidée, dégustation et restaurant panoramique.\nDécouvrez la plus ancienne plantation de thé de Maurice et plongez dans l'histoire de la production du thé mauricien. La visite comprend le musée du thé, l'usine de fabrication et une dégustation avec une vue panoramique exceptionnelle sur les plantations et le lac du sud de l'île.","descEn":"Mauritius's oldest tea plantation, in operation since 1892. Guided tour, tasting and panoramic restaurant.\n\nDiscover Mauritius' oldest tea plantation and learn about the island's tea making heritage. The visit includes the tea museum, factory tour and a tea tasting experience with stunning panoramic views over the plantations and surrounding lake.","address":"Bois Chéri Road, Bois Chéri, Savanne, Mauritius","phone":"+230 601 8000","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4263291,57.5256586","image":"https://www.atomleisure.mu/media/catalog/product/cache/1/thumbnail/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/r/r/rr-processx-image.jpg","distance":"30mins","priceLevel":"Rs 500 à Rs 250","openHours":""},{"id":"rxpcqjn2","nameFr":"Gris Gris Beach","nameEn":"Gris Gris Beach","descFr":"Plage sauvage du sud battue par les vagues de l'océan Indien. Paysage dramatique et grandiose pour les amateurs de nature brute.\nContrairement aux plages protégées par le récif corallien, Gris Gris est l'un des rares endroits de Maurice où l'océan Indien se déchaîne directement contre les falaises. Célèbre pour ses vagues spectaculaires, ses falaises abruptes et son paysage sauvage, ce site offre l'un des panoramas côtiers les plus impressionnants de l'île.","descEn":"Wild southern beach battered by Indian Ocean waves. Dramatic, grand landscape for nature lovers.\nUnlike most Mauritian beaches protected by coral reefs, Gris Gris is one of the few places where the Indian Ocean crashes directly against dramatic cliffs. Famous for its powerful waves, rugged coastline and breathtaking scenery, it offers one of the island's most spectacular coastal viewpoints.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.5243899,57.5322158","image":"https://mauritiusattractions.com/content/images/gallery/1829/gris-gris-coastal-hike-river-trek-south-mauritius%20(1).jpg","distance":"30mins","priceLevel":"Free","openHours":""}],"coverPhoto":"https://mauritiusnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Underwater-waterfall-Le-Morne-Mauritius.jpg"},{"id":"boulangeries","nameFr":"Pâtisseries / Boulangeries","nameEn":"Bakeries / Pastry Shops","icon":"🥐","color":"#c47a3a","items":[{"id":"h4huodrd3","nameFr":"Patisserie Mahe","nameEn":"Mahe Bakery","descFr":"L'une des pâtisseries les plus connues de Mahébourg, appréciée pour ses viennoiseries fraîches, pâtisseries artisanales, gâteaux, pains et spécialités locales. Une excellente adresse pour le petit déjeuner, une pause gourmande ou pour découvrir les saveurs locales dans une ambiance authentique du Sud Est mauricien.","descEn":"One of the most popular bakeries in Mahébourg, known for its fresh pastries, artisan cakes, breads and local specialties. A great stop for breakfast, a sweet treat or to experience authentic Mauritian bakery traditions in the South East region.","address":"Rue des Cent Gaulettes, Mahébourg, Mauritius","phone":"+230 631 3927","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=Patisserie+Mahe+Mahebourg","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFTjSoPQEqYdNJ1D4w52QyFZY0sqas72UmM25-710RwkijKuX0Dngx1KbOFyuIIpo14pFZ_M5Y0I55-CBAW2tNLDSXnAI5ydCe1l8aehU4kNmU-Lp8wdbxPzbanTwcVBk1brgJs=s1360-w1360-h1020-rw","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""},{"id":"9vb08zce0","nameFr":"La Flûte Enchantée Bakery","nameEn":"La Flûte Enchantée Bakery","descFr":"Boulangerie emblématique de Mahébourg, appréciée pour son pain frais, ses viennoiseries, pâtisseries artisanales et spécialités locales. Très populaire auprès des habitants du Sud Est, c'est une excellente adresse pour un petit déjeuner authentique ou pour acheter des produits frais avant une journée à la plage ou en excursion.","descEn":"A well known bakery in Mahébourg, loved for its fresh bread, pastries, baked goods and local specialties. Popular among locals, it is a great stop for breakfast or to pick up fresh treats before heading to the beach or exploring the South East region.","address":"","phone":"+230 631 9871","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=La+Flute+Enchantee+Mahebourg","image":"https://scontent.fmru7-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/468527298_1939292019815529_8593592585242210108_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=833d8c&_nc_ohc=0TQO8ij8p9QQ7kNvwFnRSVZ&_nc_oc=Adpy4FFMMlJb8GilMQ6FVJk4XuFKKbQo73z24rx9WjeW0crlvvAh6bmhwIkTENphUqA&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fmru7-1.fna&_nc_gid=dytDuJneWIKiiW8-xtcCpQ&_nc_ss=7b2a8&oh=00_Af7q410ZFZezDY-oF4NT6oxeZxDKnESYbkNHt0vnxfNZ9Q&oe=6A20DEEA","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":"04h00 à 12h00"},{"id":"ljbiima5","nameFr":"Blé D'or Boulangerie et Patisserie","nameEn":"Blé D'or Boulangerie et Patisserie","descFr":"Boulangerie artisanale mauricienne avec pains chauds, viennoiseries et gâteaux locaux. Idéale pour le petit-déjeuner.","descEn":"Mauritian artisan bakery with warm breads, pastries and local cakes. Perfect for breakfast.","address":"","phone":"","mapLink":"https://maps.google.com/?q=-20.4319106,57.6613918","image":"https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxC0c-g3F5dfvmzmnPBPZGu1grmyQ9h4zZMGfeO-S-5wKE8anzwtR_w2L7gAHopUe_Hz7mpcEsUDDmdRghzkaic0N8Nfvh4QsDSD5sffaj3Jz58lbSpF-CcbENmUEm8bo6nFmOeRpU2ouEcB7Leka5-oCHalo7CjOkqPF3T7wWOQzbqhSYidV8AgBoHlMPJn-IpQ8xz7gep?authuser=0&fife=s16383","distance":"","priceLevel":"","openHours":""}],"coverPhoto":"https://cdn-i2.starofservice.com/images/annubis/services/service-de-patisserie.webp"}],"subcategori